headline: These 7 Stocks Are Analyst Favorites For Magnificent Earnings Growth
summary: Netflix and DoorDash are two of the seven best stocks where investors can find magnificent profit growth prospects.  More than 70% of analysts covering Netflix have buy or overweight ratings on the video streaming service.  The consensus estimate for 2025 earnings is $24.69, a 25% increase from last year.
